fields.Title: BOARDWALK / PAYPHONE
fields.Description: Payphone, for calling folk. Call everyone.

fields.Title: You: ""Yes, it's me -- Pierre.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, it's me -- Pierre."

fields.Title: You: ""Yes, Pierre is dead.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, Pierre is dead."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""But who are you then? A salesman o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But who are you then? A salesman of some sort? Modern goods are rubbish. And I can't afford them anyhow. It's a shame what you did to our country..." The woman moans and the phone lines howl in unison with her.

fields.Title: Payphone: "Her voice is drowned in white noise..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her voice is drowned in white noise. Sounds like waves washing a beach, growing in volume until the call suddenly disconnects.

fields.Title: You: "Keep dialling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Keep dialling...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""You shouldn't mess with people lik..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You shouldn't mess with people like this..." His voice is very calm. "You go have a nice day now."

fields.Title: You: ""Guillaume. Guillaume le Million.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Guillaume. Guillaume le Million."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Harry, please..." A sad voice answ..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Harry, please..." A sad voice answers, dressed in distortion.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You were making *prank calls*." No..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You were making *prank calls*." Not a muscle moves in the lieutenant's face.

fields.Title: Payphone: ""My *debt?* I don't fucking owe you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My *debt?* I don't fucking owe you, it's..." The young man realises something. "Who is... ah never mind, I don't have time for this..."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Life is garbage."
fields.Dialogue Text: Life is garbage.

fields.Title: Empathy: "He accepts your apology."
fields.Dialogue Text: He accepts your apology.

fields.Title: Empathy: "The saddest sound in the world."
fields.Dialogue Text: The saddest sound in the world.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm not drunk.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm not drunk."

fields.Title: You: ""I want to talk about me. Who am I?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I want to talk about me. Who am I? You sound like you know me."

fields.Title: Volition: "Right now. I'm gonna give you *one*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Right now. I'm gonna give you *one* chance.

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "In the distorted distance you hear..."
fields.Dialogue Text: In the distorted distance you hear someone turning next to her. Bedsprings rattle.

fields.Title: Payphone: ""So nice of you to find the time to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So nice of you to find the time to call me! It gets so lonely. Even the animals have died."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""He's my sister's grandson. He used..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He's my sister's grandson. He used to visit me as a lad... Fine young man..."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""This is because we are bred to be..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "This is because we are bred to be leaders. I can hear the common or mixed background from your voice."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""You're either a salesman or a stat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're either a salesman or a statistician of some kind. I am not interested in cooperating."

fields.Title: Authority: "Again? Seriously?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Again? Seriously?

fields.Title: You: ""I don't know why I said that.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know why I said that."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""What are you, like five?" A woman'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What are you, like five?" A woman's voice shouts something in the background and when Girard speaks again his voice is hushed...

fields.Title: You: "Finish it."
fields.Dialogue Text: Finish it.

fields.Title: Volition: "Now walk away. Forget about this. W..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Now walk away. Forget about this. Walk away and do police work. *BURY* this in yourself and move on.

fields.Title: Authority: "Before it's too late, please."
fields.Dialogue Text: Before it's too late, please.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "What were you trying to achieve by..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What were you trying to achieve by closing your eyes? Did you want your muscle memory to take over and call somewhere? Where?

fields.Title: Half Light: "Pitiful and terrifying. You feel yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Pitiful and terrifying. You feel your pulse rise with each ring...

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Interfacing: "You dialled 001. This is not the ar..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You dialled 001. This is not the area code of Revachol. It is another destination -- on another isola. Some far-off nation state.

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Fuck it, it doesn't hurt."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fuck it, it doesn't hurt.

fields.Title: Payphone: "A metal payphone under a yellow pla..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A metal payphone under a yellow plastic dome. There's a bitter, caustic taste on the tip of your tongue as you look at the handset.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothGrab); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothGrab); HideActualHeld();

fields.Title: Drama: "What *you* are is a *surprise*, get..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What *you* are is a *surprise*, get his wife on the phone...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Writing. I hate writing so much......"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Writing. I hate writing so much... But I have to get back to it."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Is that you?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is that you?"

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Yes, I'm in Mirova. Sleeping.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, I'm in Mirova. Sleeping."

fields.Title: You: ""My heart hurts. I'm gonna have a h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "My heart hurts. I'm gonna have a heart attack."
fields.Alternate1: "My heart hurts. I'm gonna have another heart attack."

fields.Title: You: "Pick up the handset."
fields.Dialogue Text: Pick up the handset.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothGrab); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothGrab); HideActualHeld();

fields.Title: Payphone: "You hear the tone -- the machine is..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You hear the tone -- the machine is operable.

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""You ruined it and you sold it to f..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You ruined it and you sold it to foreigners. You don't own anything if everything is for sale."

fields.Title: You: ""Get away from her, I'm a cop!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Get away from her, I'm a cop!"

fields.Title: Payphone: "You can't make out a single word, j..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can't make out a single word, just vague voices. One more, a child, has joined. Something breaks -- or falls over? Footsteps approaching!

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What the hell are you doing?" The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What the hell are you doing?" The lieutenant has been keeping a distance, but steps closer now.

fields.Title: You: ""You seem to be in some sort of tro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You seem to be in some sort of trouble. Maybe I can help you, I'm a police officer."

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "You just do. And you know it is goi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You just do. And you know it is going to hurt.

fields.Title: Horrific Necktie: "Yeah, *bratan*. We've had all the f..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yeah, *bratan*. We've had all the fun there was to have here. And it wasn't much.

fields.Title: Payphone: "It didn't give you *any* fun for th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It didn't give you *any* fun for that money.

fields.Title: Volition: "You can't. Some strange force is ke..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can't. Some strange force is keeping the headset glued to your hand, your ear listening to the ring in the speaker...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""You're not an amnesiac, Harry... Y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're not an amnesiac, Harry... You're drunk."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm not drunk -- I'm *high*.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm not drunk -- I'm *high*."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""I don't understand what you're say..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't understand what you're saying."

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "Twenty-two million people live in M..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Twenty-two million people live in Mirova, the capital city of Graad. It is the capital of the world after Revachol was destroyed.

fields.Title: Payphone: "End of tone. Someone picks up."
fields.Dialogue Text: End of tone. Someone picks up.

fields.Title: You: "Put 10 cents in and dial a random n..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Put 10 cents in and dial a random number: 005-24-03-155.
fields.Sequence: AudioPlay(boardwalk/payphone/coin-inserted-01,1); PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothDial); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothDial);

fields.Title: You: ""You're naked, aren't you?" (Beat t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're naked, aren't you?" (Beat the handset against the phone.)

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Wh-who is this?" The man does not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wh-who is this?" The man does not understand.

fields.Title: Payphone: "More shouting. You're pretty sure y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: More shouting. You're pretty sure you hear a man saying *fuck* several times. Then the crackle in the phone line gets violently loud, like the surf breaking.

fields.Title: You: "Keep dialling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Keep dialling...

fields.Title: Jump to: [Kim Kitsuragi: ""Big deal?!" Not a muscle moves in..."]
You: "(Hang up.)"
fields.Dialogue Text: (Hang up.)

fields.Title: Payphone: "She does not answer anymore."
fields.Dialogue Text: She does not answer anymore.

fields.Title: You: ""It gets lonely even when you're wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It gets lonely even when you're with people."

fields.Title: Payphone: "You dial the number again -- as you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You dial the number again -- as you've done many times. You remember it well now: 001 -- 41 -- 44 -- 47 -- 11 -- 17 -- 361 -- 451 -- 67 -- 451 -- 451.

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Are you sure you're Pierre? Your v..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Are you sure you're Pierre? Your voice, it's different... I... there... chrysanthemum..."

fields.Title: You: "Hang up. [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: Hang up. [Leave.]
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothHangup); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothHangup);

fields.Title: Empathy: "It looks like she does not want to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It looks like she does not want to pick it up, Harry. Stop scaring her.

fields.Title: You: ""I am the last faithful kingsman. I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am the last faithful kingsman. I will free the city of Revachol. I will turn back the sea. I will reverse time." (Proceed.)

fields.Title: Payphone: "In the middle of it -- a familiar r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: In the middle of it -- a familiar ring. Small. Distorted.

fields.Title: Payphone: "And calling -- for two minutes now...."
fields.Dialogue Text: And calling -- for two minutes now. You're out of luck. No one's home there either. But the payphone still has your ten cents in there...

fields.Title: Payphone: "You pick up the handset. There's a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You pick up the handset. There's a tone -- the machine is operable.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothGrab); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothGrab); HideActualHeld();

fields.Title: Payphone: "Then the ocean breaks. Out of the d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Then the ocean breaks. Out of the depths, a woman's voice emerges. Small. The dearest thing you've ever heard.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm not drunk or high, I'm just......"
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm not drunk or high, I'm just... hurt... why does it hurt to talk to you?"

fields.Title: Payphone: "Static sings inside the phone glued..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Static sings inside the phone glued to your ear. Ancient, sticky...

fields.Title: Payphone: "She does not answer. All you hear i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She does not answer. All you hear is hiss.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Dora. The name feels like a *gift*...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Dora. The name feels like a *gift*. A gift that was meant for you -- to make it possible to live.

fields.Title: You: ""No, I'm a police officer.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I'm a police officer."

fields.Title: You: ""Good bye.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Good bye."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Payphone: "The headset lands in the cradle wit..."]
You: "Just let it ring."
fields.Dialogue Text: Just let it ring.

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You're right, you shouldn't have.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're right, you shouldn't have."

fields.Title: You: ""We could all be a bit kinder to ea..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We could all be a bit kinder to each other, don't you think? Consider your debt paid, my friend."

fields.Title: Payphone: "The phone gets hanged up fast as li..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The phone gets hanged up fast as lightning, all you hear is a little shuffle of nylon as the hand moves on the other end.

fields.Title: Endurance: "The handset starts slipping from yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The handset starts slipping from your sweaty palm... your breathing is heavy.

fields.Title: You: "Stop!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Stop!

fields.Title: You: ""You want my MONEY?!" (Punch the ph..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You want my MONEY?!" (Punch the phone.)
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothHangup); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothHangup); PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, GenericPunch)@2; PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothGrab)@6.25; PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothGrab)@6.25;

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant is too far away to h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant is too far away to hear your yelp. The sea wind blows...

fields.Title: You: "Let it call more."
fields.Dialogue Text: Let it call more.

fields.Title: You: ""Okay I'm drunk, what does it matte..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay I'm drunk, what does it matter? I'm still *me*!"

fields.Title: Volition: "You need to stop, Harry. You'll die..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You need to stop, Harry. You'll die.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm gonna solve it.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm gonna solve it."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""You're not a revolutionary, Harry...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're not a revolutionary, Harry... You're drunk."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""What a pity... I'm afraid I won't..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What a pity... I'm afraid I won't be coming to the funeral. I.... there... chrysanthemum..."

fields.Title: You: ""A creature is a creature. I wish I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A creature is a creature. I wish I was the wind."

fields.Title: You: ""Your voice makes me want to turn i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Your voice makes me want to turn into dust."

fields.Title: You: ""I am an ultra-high-net-worth indiv..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am an ultra-high-net-worth individual. I understand how reality works. I have *seen* into it. My mind is clear." (Proceed.)

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: "The headset lands in the cradle wit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The headset lands in the cradle with a clank.

fields.Title: You: "Hang up."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hang up.

fields.Title: You: ""Who is this?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who is this?"

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""You're not a kingsman, Harry... Yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're not a kingsman, Harry... You're drunk."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""You're not ominous, Harry... You'r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're not ominous, Harry... You're drunk."

fields.Title: Interfacing: "41 -- 44 -- 47 -- the rotary dial f..."
fields.Dialogue Text: 41 -- 44 -- 47 -- the rotary dial feels cold from the sea air.

fields.Title: You: "Long windows... how do I know that?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Long windows... how do I know that?

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Who cares. Run. Go. Don't think abo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Who cares. Run. Go. Don't think about this. Do police work, it's all there is.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Khm..." A single *khm* lets you kn..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Khm..." A single *khm* lets you know the lieutenant is ready to move now.

fields.Title: Payphone: ""I'm tired..." A man answers, fast..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm tired..." A man answers, fast this time. His voice is hoarse from cigarettes. You hear typing in the background.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm tired too.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm tired too."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "He doesn't have a home. His home is..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He doesn't have a home. His home is under a boat.

fields.Title: Payphone: ""The Academy. Where I work.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The Academy. Where I work."

fields.Title: You: "I'm making a funny prank call."
fields.Dialogue Text: I'm making a funny prank call.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Push the headset in the cradle with..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Push the headset in the cradle with all the strength you have!

fields.Title: You: ""None of it matters -- not anymore.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "None of it matters -- not anymore."

fields.Title: Payphone: "The cord dangles in the wind like a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The cord dangles in the wind like a sickening worm.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothHangupDora); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothHangupDora);

fields.Title: You: ""I'm not a salesman, I was just cal..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm not a salesman, I was just calling a random number and you somehow ran with it."

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Volition: "Don't react. Whatever you do, don't..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Don't react. Whatever you do, don't react to that last thing.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You get a sinking feeling. It makes..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You get a sinking feeling. It makes you look if Lieutenant Kitsuragi overheard you. To your relief, he did not.

fields.Title: You: ""You're warm.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're warm."

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Hello, Girard speaking!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hello, Girard speaking!"

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Thanks for calling, asshole!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks for calling, asshole!"

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Mhm," she hums, her voice warm fro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mhm," she hums, her voice warm from sleep.

fields.Title: You: ""You're right, Kim -- it went wrong..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're right, Kim -- it went wrong. Horribly wrong. I shouldn't have done this..." (Hang up.)

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Strange. This is not how you starte..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Strange. This is not how you started before.

fields.Title: Volition: "What in the name of god did you jus..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What in the name of god did you just do?

fields.Title: Interfacing: "451 -- you have dialled god knows h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: 451 -- you have dialled god knows how many numbers. The headset has been waiting silently to relay a signal -- surely nothing can come of this, you think. But it does. A connection.

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: "There's a moment of silence before..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There's a moment of silence before the voice speaks again, more calmly: "You got the wrong number, don't call here again."

fields.Title: Payphone: "Time keeps passing. In the distance..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Time keeps passing. In the distance, seagulls squawk -- no one is home at this number. But the coin... it's still in there... you find yourself thinking:

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Again you close your eyes -- and ag..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Again you close your eyes -- and again your fingers move on the rotary dial. Ten metallic rings as the dial returns to zero after each number.

fields.Title: Drama: "No, what *you* are is a *surprise*,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, what *you* are is a *surprise*, get his wife on the phone...

fields.Title: You: ""I don't know who I am. I am an amn..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know who I am. I am an amnesiac." (Proceed.)

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: IsHighestPolitical("communist") == false  and  IsHighestPolitical("revacholian_nationhood") == false  and  IsHighestPolitical("ultraliberal") == false  and  IsHighestPolitical("moralist") == false

fields.Title: Payphone: "Still..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Still...

fields.Title: You: ""Harry? How do you know my name?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Harry? How do you know my name?"

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Oh no... please stop. Please let's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh no... please stop. Please let's just hang up..."

fields.Title: Payphone: "She sighs. "Look, I don't understan..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She sighs. "Look, I don't understand what you're saying, or why you're calling me. You seem drunk."

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothHangup); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothHangup); ShowActualHeld()@3;

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Do you have any news about Pierre?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you have any news about Pierre?"

fields.Title: Payphone: "You can't hear her reply."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can't hear her reply.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Yes. 451 -- 67 -- 451 -- you are go..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes. 451 -- 67 -- 451 -- you are going deeper now, into some unknown place. Far away from this island of matter and its telecommunication networks....

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "No answer. You're not sure but you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No answer. You're not sure but you think you hear a *man's* voice in the background. It's covered in pain and white noise...

fields.Title: Payphone: "Phone hanging up."
fields.Dialogue Text: Phone hanging up.

fields.Title: You: "Put 10 cents in and dial a random n..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Put 10 cents in and dial a random number: 005-99-77-313.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothDial); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothDial);

fields.Title: You: ""Hey, Girard, get your wife for me,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hey, Girard, get your wife for me, will you?"

fields.Title: You: ""Girard... what a douche name... Ch..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Girard... what a douche name... Change it -- change your name!"

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: "The sounds are muffled. You can mak..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The sounds are muffled. You can make out two people: a man and a woman called *Bian*. They are talking to each other in agitated voices. There's a shuffle of feet, children maybe?

fields.Title: Payphone: "Something hits the phone with a lou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Something hits the phone with a loud crack of plastic and microphone hiss -- after that you are left with the disconnect tone.

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "Home?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Home?

fields.Title: You: "Put 10 cents in and dial the long p..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Put 10 cents in and dial the long phone number again.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothDial); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothDial);

fields.Title: Volition: "That's right. You *can*. Whatever y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That's right. You *can*. Whatever you're doing here, you can just stop it and go on with your life.

fields.Title: Jump to: [Payphone: "No response, only a sigh. The conne..."]
Payphone: ""To work.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "To work."

fields.Title: You: ""I am the law. I'm a detective. I'm..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am the law. I'm a detective. I'm doing a case. There's a hanged man."

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Give it a thought. Goodbye.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Give it a thought. Goodbye."

fields.Title: You: ""I need answers to my *mystery*.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I need answers to my *mystery*."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm sorry it was a stupid joke, I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm sorry it was a stupid joke, I shouldn't have called, it's stupid -- I'm so sorry."

fields.Title: You: ""Pick it up!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Pick it up!"

fields.Title: Empathy: "C'mon, you know why."
fields.Dialogue Text: C'mon, you know why.

fields.Title: You: ""I'm the guy who's fucking your wif..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm the guy who's fucking your wife, Girard. Now put her on before I lose my patience."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm Mazov. Kraz Mazov.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm Mazov. Kraz Mazov."

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Who is this?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who is this?"

fields.Title: You: "Let it call!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Let it call!

fields.Title: Payphone: "*Still* calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: *Still* calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Hello." She sounds sleepy."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hello." She sounds sleepy.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothCallDora)@2; PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothCallDora)@2;

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling...

fields.Title: Payphone: "There's still some unused change in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There's still some unused change in there -- the machine waits for a number to be dialled.
fields.Sequence: PlayAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PhoneboothGrab); PlayAnimation(Phone Booth, PhoneboothGrab); HideActualHeld();

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Punch it again, the pain is good."
fields.Dialogue Text: Punch it again, the pain is good.

fields.Title: Payphone: "Calling in the night...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Calling in the night....

fields.Title: Payphone: ""I'll get you your money, alright?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'll get you your money, alright? I just need 'til tonight. Let me work."

fields.Title: Payphone: "Disconnect tone."
fields.Dialogue Text: Disconnect tone.

fields.Title: You: ""Harry? Who's Harry -- are you slee..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Harry? Who's Harry -- are you sleeping with him? I'm also Harry!"

fields.Title: Payphone: ""Do you know what time it is? It's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know what time it is? It's so late here..." Sounds like she's looking for a clock on the night stand.

fields.Title: You: ""Ooo... are you there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ooo... are you there?"

fields.Title: You: ""Where are you? You sound like you'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where are you? You sound like you're in another world."

fields.Title: Volition: "You need to stop. Harry. You're kil..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You need to stop. Harry. You're killing yourself.

fields.Title: You: ""Is someone there with you?""
